## Architecture Notes

### SMTP 发送流程
  net.Dial(smtp_host:port) → STARTTLS → Auth(PlainAuth) → Mail → Rcpt → Data → Quit
  优雅降级: SMTP_HOST="" → NewEmailNotifier() 返回 nil → 不发送邮件
  认证失败: 记录 Warn 日志，尝试无认证继续

### 告警触发点 (当前)
  - Kill Switch Engage: SRE handler POST /api/admin/sre/killswitch/engage
  后续可接入:
  - NATS "account.margin_call" → MarginCallAlert
  - Strategy Breaker RecordPnL → BreakerTripAlert
  - Canary Promote → PromoteToLiveAlert
  - RateLimit 拦截 → AnomalyAlert

### 配置示例 (docker-compose 环境变量)
  SMTP_HOST=smtp.example.com
  SMTP_PORT=587
  SMTP_USER=alerts@example.com
  SMTP_PASSWORD=***
  SMTP_FROM="Ant Alerts <alerts@example.com>"
  SMTP_TO=admin@company.com,oncall@company.com

